data.description: Wonderful 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom Ranch on 1.25 acres with NO HOA! Enter into the large family room with vaulted ceilings and fireplace.  Kitchen features white cabinets and spacious breakfast room.  Separate formal dining room.  One bedroom with private ensuite.  3bedrooms, full bath and master bedroom.  Master bath has dual vanities, soaker tub and separate shower.  Upstairs feature a very large bonus room, could be used as another bedroom.  Large, private backyard fenced in with a huge outbuilding.  Priced  to sell.  Book your appointment today.
